01:58:55,462 --> 01:58:56,411
Mételo a fuerzas!

1856
01:58:57,447 --> 01:59:00,262
239!
239.5!

1857
01:59:00,487 --> 01:59:01,436
Directo!

1858
01:59:01,703 --> 01:59:03,613
240.5!
Harry!

1859
01:59:04,968 --> 01:59:06,244
Lo logramos!

